data.description: Majestic oak trees surround the home on its coveted corner lot. Inside, the living room has a vaulted ceiling, lots of light, and a ceiling fan that keeps the air circulating. The kitchen has warm, honey-toned cabinetry and a pass-through to the living room. A separate dining area is great for both formal and casual dining. The laundry room has extra storage space. There are three bedrooms, the main bedroom has an ensuite bathroom, and the other two bedrooms share a second bathroom. A partially covered back patio and a large, fully fenced-in backyard are great for outdoor living. The oversized, detached garage has room for storage and a workshop with a paved circular driveway.
